sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as Linux Agent
    participant Server as Fastify Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant WS as WebSocket Hub
    participant UI as Dashboard

    Agent->>Agent: Collect /proc metrics
    Agent->>Agent: Run security collectors
    Agent->>Server: Send binary frame
    Server->>Server: Decode frame by type
    Server->>DB: Persist metrics/report/event
    Server->>Server: Run correlation rules
    Server->>WS: Broadcast invalidation
    UI->>Server: Request updated snapshot
    Server->>UI: Return latest data
